    "On the other hand, EmoSenticNet and WordNet-Affect were both built on a large lexical database of English (Miller, 1998) and, thus, included more words that appear in our dataset.",
    "While NRC includes words such as \"whimsical\" or \"pleased\" in relation to \"joy,\" the other two RMDs also feature \"cool\" and \"awesome.\"",
    "Additionally, our CMD included the internet-specific \"lol,\" which is likely to be particularly relevant when analyzing Reddit posts.",
